headline: RTX to release first quarter earnings results on April 22, 2025
summary: RTX (NYSE: RTX) will issue its first quarter 2025 earnings results on Tuesday, April 22, prior to the stock market opening. A conference call will take place at 8:30 a.m. ET to discuss the results.
